    &nbsp; 
  </div> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p></p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 id="toc2" class="bonfire"><a name="x--Notes"></a>Notes</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Deals fire damage</li> 
 <li>Very short range (visual is longer than real hitbox)</li> 
 <li>Around 3 secs windup</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
